scripting maily depends upon the combination of commands
most commonly used  commands in scripting are sed awk grep and find command.
sed command is something which allows you to replace, remove, add any strings and line inside the file without opening it.
awk commands is somthing which allows you to manupilate the words in the file. IN other words it allows high level of filteration for file strings .

grep command is something which allows you to filter particular string inside the file 
find command is something we all are aware of. Find command is not just a simple tool to search anything by name ! you can filter searching using options like size, file type, name, empty files, permission, and many more ! 
